<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3715846>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Wing venation of Succinoraphidia radioni sp. nov., holotype SIZK L-105. A, left forewing; B, right forewing; C, left hind wing; D, right hind wing (A and C converted to standard view, with apex to the right). Fused veins are shown by red lines. Scale bar = 2 mm (all to scale)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3715846/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

